{"tid":2197770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[新彊木蘭] Reuters: 中國禁止有關《Mulan》報導","createTime":"2020-09-11T01:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T16:59:19.000Z","uid":67340,"like":184,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"28875e595f34f8f9c070363247a799b7487dddd7","tid":2197770,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T01:01:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">睇新聞學英文</span></span>，<span class=\"gold\">星期一至五</span>簡單翻譯一至兩篇外國報導，等大家可以<span class=\"gold\">雙語</span>吸收資訊，學多啲英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其係咁多位DSE仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">一於齊上齊學</span></span><br />\n孫某做project做到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望睇完幫手Like+推，鍾意就Dog/follow埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-film-mulan-china-exclusive/exclusive-china-bars-media-coverage-of-disneys-mulan-after-xinjiang-backlash-sources-idUSKBN2611FP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-film-mulan-china-exclusive%2Fexclusive-china-bars-media-coverage-of-disneys-mulan-after-xinjiang-backlash-sources-idUSKBN2611FP&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=56a2bf8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-film-mulan-china-exclusive%2Fexclusive-china-bars-media-coverage-of-disneys-mulan-after-xinjiang-backlash-sources-idUSKBN2611FP&h=1a357d94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-film-mulan-china-exclusive/exclusive-china-bars-media-coverage-of-disneys-mulan-after-xinjiang-backlash-sources-idUSKBN2611FP</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">Exclusive: China bars media coverage of Disney's 'Mulan' after Xinjiang backlash - sources</span><br />\n<br />\n//Chinese authorities have told major media outlets<span class=\"red\"> not to cover</span> Walt Disney Co&rsquo;s release of &ldquo;Mulan&rdquo;, in an order issued after controversy erupted overseas over the film&rsquo;s links with the Xinjiang region, four people familiar with matter told Reuters.//<br />\n「根據4名消息人士，《Mulan》因為同新彊嘅關係喺海外引起爭議後，中國當局叫媒體<span class=\"red\">唔好報導</span>《Mulan》上映。」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Erupt</span>係爆發，形容火山噴發，引申至公眾情緒，輿論既爆發，同義詞有 arise (出現), <span class=\"orange\">ignite (點燃), break out, flare up</span>。<br />\n<br />\n//No reason was given in the notice, but the sources said they believed it was because of <span class=\"red\">the overseas backlash</span> over the film&rsquo;s links to Xinjiang. //<br />\n「個通告冇講過係咩原因，但消息人士話佢地信係因為<span class=\"red\">海外圍屌</span>《Mulan》同新彊嘅關係。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//Partly shot in Xinjiang, <span class=\"red\">Mulan&rsquo;s credits included thanks to the authorities there</span>, which prompted calls overseas for a boycott of the movie. China&rsquo;s clampdown on ethnic Uighurs and other Muslims in Xinjiang has been criticised by some governments, including the United States, and human rights groups. //<br />\n「因為有部分喺新彊拍，《Mulan》<span class=\"red\">片尾有對當地部門既鳴謝</span>，導致海外發起杯葛。中國對當地維吾爾人同其他穆斯林既打壓一直被其他政府批評，包括美國，仲有其他人權組織。」<br />\n<br />\n希望睇完幫手Like+推，鍾意就Dog/follow埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n相關翻譯:<br />\n[雖遠必誅] BBC: 美國對新彊出口實施禁令<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2196041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2196041</a><br />\n<br />\n[全球霸權] BBC: 中國綁架印度公民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192853</a><br />\n<br />\n[出清國記] 澳洲廣播公司：澳中5日外交僵局 最後兩名記者走得甩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2193529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2193529</a>"},{"pid":"aff97abb1968af89838f8be428fce231115c7dbf","tid":2197770,"uid":67340,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T01:01:46.000Z","msg":"孫某要求各位DSE仔女努力讀書，多睇英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec11d2e452b1a0b5412b932787fea3a7be2f966","tid":2197770,"uid":67340,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T01:02:00.000Z","msg":"孫某近排多左功課做可能會冇咁準時<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望見諒"},{"pid":"45c39b32991354f678e191c55bfe36722e85ed0c","tid":2197770,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T01:02:20.000Z","msg":"唔準宣傳，但準播<br />\n弱智國家"},{"pid":"c35f91896d8facb1332ff04f5ee31eaaed7d120a","tid":2197770,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T01:02:43.000Z","msg":"好早<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47713ba658d7cdf31bcd3b67e37a28ea254db4c4","tid":2197770,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T01:02: